  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "STORE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>A Food Store Supervisor oversees daily operations, staff, and inventory to ensure efficient service, high food safety standards, and customer satisfaction<br /></p><p>Responsibilities:<br /></p><ul><li>Supervise daily store activities, including opening/closing, and ensure strict compliance with health, safety, and sanitation regulations.</li><li>Hire, train, schedule, and motivate employees, monitoring performance to meet company standards.</li><li>Monitor stock levels, order supplies, manage, and inspect inventory for quality, reducing waste and preventing theft.</li><li>Address and resolve customer complaints, inquiries, and requests in a professional manner.</li><li>Manage cash, monitor sales, and assist with budget control.</li></ul><p>Qualifications: <br /></p><ul><li>Years of experience in a supervisory role within a food store.</li><li>Strong leadership, communication, organizational, and problem-solving abilities.</li><li>Familiarity with food safety regulations and inventory management systems.</li><li>Ability to work, weekends, holidays, and extended hours as needed.</li></ul>",
